text: Kitada (written: 北田) is a Japanese surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Akihiro Kitada (born 1971), Japanese sociologist * Akiko Kitada (born 1982), Japanese former field hockey player * Kayo Kitada (born 1978), retired Japanese judoka * Rui Kitada (born 1981), Japanese professional golfer Category:Japanese-language surnames
